data.description: Stunning Megatel Home 4 bedrooms, 3 baths in Grayhawk! Coleman II Bronze Series. The open concept floorplan is perfect for entertaining guests boasting a spectacular kitchen complete with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, & over-sized island with breakfast bar and easily flows into the large living area. Light & bright open concept space has beautiful views of the backyard offering plenty of room for pets & play! Master suite allows for easy relaxation consisting of dual sinks, soaking tub & separate shower! Amazing amenities including community pool & park! This home is a MUST SEE!
